entries.title: Same but Different
entries.entry:
I remember being stressed out about our Coffee Shop project.....oh how I miss those days!

However, I have picked up a skill in this bootcamp that will last me a lifetime - to laugh off the stress. 

Life keeps going, stress only slows you down and you'll be even more behind if you take the time to listen to the voices in your head.
